    "Support vector machines, naive Bayes, and artificial neural networks are used to classify these features.",
    "Accuracy, average precision, and average recall are used to compare each classifier's performance.",
    "The key achievement of Kose et al. [83] is the identification of time domain features as the optimal characteristics for EOG and EMG data using the ANN classifier to achieve maximum classification accuracy.",
